Netizen contribution
Around 10:00 on June 3, near Yongzheng West Street, Shifang City, Deyang, Sichuan, a man stabbed a woman with a knife in the street. Eyewitness Mr. Liu said that the incident happened at the door of a roadside pharmacy. The man stabbed the woman with a knife. After being stabbed, the woman lay on the ground without moving. Then, the man scratched his neck with a knife and fell on the stabbed woman.
The picture shows that the police arrived at the scene to handle the situation and maintain order. At around 13:00, the local police station said that the two had been sent to the hospital and the incident was being handled.
